The paper also discusses wireless channels and channel state information, which are relevant to the Signal Processing (cs.SI) and Multimedia (cs.MM) sub-categories. Finally, the paper touches on secret-key agreement, which falls under the Network and Internet Architecture (cs.NI) sub-category.
